SWIPE ➡️ Arda Güler has hit back against Dominik Szoboszlai, after the Liverpool star commented ‘1088,” on his Instagram, highlighting the number of minutes Arda has played this season...

🗣️“This guy is a joke. Isn’t 6 goals enough to shut you up?🤫”

He also added “1 Instagram comment Szoboszlai” to the scoreboard on his post 😂
